reviews.text: Long way to car park, parking application not working, When you in rush that is worst place to be. Hate to park here.

Gotta be desperate for staff to hire that fat jobsworth who stands at the barriers most nights. Never been there without seeing him starting on someone un-necessarily. Wouldn’t even let a mother through the barriers with her 4/5 year made the child go round the side on his own unsupervised. Zero customer service and the rudest man i’ve ever met. get off your high horse mate you look like a thumb

Today I got treated badly by the fat member of staff today. My Oyster card was working and he denied it wasn’t working, 10-15 mins later another member off staff looked at my Oyster card and it said it went tho. My time was wasted I was going to s doctors appoment which I was late for. Got very bad customer service I’m not happy the way I got treated and wasn’t happy the way it got handled. Very rude and not helpful. 8/02/2018 around 4-5 pm . That fat man with the glasses.
